snippet.textDisplay:
Everytime I listen this song, I cry because of the picturisation I get in my Mind from my memories about my Sister. As our father is no more. And I can express the feeling my father could bear to, if he would be alive at time of my Sister's Marraige. 
She is yet to marry. And I get overwhelmed for this unrest upcoming emotions. 

Thank you Sachin Jigar and all Musicians.
